SUMMARY:Investigate missing narratives in new batch pipeline run
DESCRIPTION:Trend narratives ran on 2026-03-24 (9 narratives) but not on 2026-03-25 post-collect run.\n\nInvestigate:\n- run_trending.py --narratives flag: is it passed in run_pipeline.py stages?\n- Is the narratives stage skipped when collect exits rc=2 (batch_pending path)?\n- Does make post-collect pass --narratives to run_trending.py?\n- Check funnel_stats for 2026-03-25 trending stage drop_reasons\n- OPENAI_API_KEY not set warning seen in screenshot — narratives currently require OpenAI; should switch to Anthropic\n\nCommands:\n  sqlite3 data/db/film.db "SELECT * FROM funnel_stats WHERE stage='trending' ORDER BY run_date DESC LIMIT 5;"\n  grep -n "narratives" scripts/run_pipeline.py\n  grep -n "narratives" scripts/run_trending.py
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:task-uzel-auth-20260325@predictor_ingest
DTSTAMP:20260325T120000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260325
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260326
SUMMARY:[easy win] Add Caddy basicauth to uzelhub-web preview
DESCRIPTION:Add Caddy basic auth to the uzelhub-web preview — single shared credential for a small trusted circle. Upgrade to Cloudflare Access later if per-user control is needed.\n\nRepo: uzelhub-web (site-wide content, hosts graph explorer web/)\n\nInfrastructure context:\n- Domain: Porkbun registered\n- DNS/proxy: Cloudflare (proxied — Hetzner IP not exposed)\n- Web server: Caddy on Hetzner\n\nImplementation (2 minutes):\n  1. Generate bcrypt hash:  caddy hash-password\n  2. Add to Caddyfile:\n       preview.uzelhub.com {\n         basicauth {\n           uzel $2a$14$<hash>\n         }\n         root * /path/to/uzelhub-web\n         file_server\n       }\n  3. caddy reload\n  4. Test with incognito window\n\nUpgrade path: swap basicauth block for Cloudflare Access when\nper-user logins are needed — no other Caddyfile changes required.
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
